{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":765,"text":"I'm a little nervous, because my wife Yvonne said to me,"},{"time":4274,"text":"she said, \"Geoff, you watch the TED Talks.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":6443,"text":"I said, \"Yes, honey, I love TED Talks.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":8379,"text":"She said, \"You know, they're like, really smart, talented -- \""}]},{"cues":[{"time":11867,"text":"I said, \"I know, I know.\" (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":13610,"text":"She said, \"They don't want, like, the angry black man.\""},{"time":18402,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":20355,"text":"So I said, \"No, I'm gonna be good, Honey,"},{"time":21966,"text":"I'm gonna be good. I am.\""},{"time":24021,"text":"But I am angry. (Laughter)"},{"time":27439,"text":"And the last time I looked, I'm --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":31145,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":33952,"text":"So this is why I'm excited but I'm angry."},{"time":39380,"text":"This year, there are going to be millions of our children"},{"time":44299,"text":"that we're going to needlessly lose,"},{"time":47263,"text":"that we could -- right now, we could save them all."},{"time":51853,"text":"You saw the quality of the educators who were here."},{"time":55698,"text":"Do not tell me they could not reach those kids"},{"time":59035,"text":"and save them. I know they could."},{"time":61306,"text":"It is absolutely possible."},{"time":64167,"text":"Why haven't we fixed this?"},{"time":66550,"text":"Those of us in education have held on to a business plan"},{"time":71314,"text":"that we don't care how many millions of young people fail,"},{"time":75169,"text":"we're going to continue to do the same thing that didn't work,"},{"time":78264,"text":"and nobody is getting crazy about it -- right? --"},{"time":83207,"text":"enough to say, \"Enough is enough.\""},{"time":85352,"text":"So here's a business plan that simply does not make any sense."}]},{"cues":[{"time":89736,"text":"You know, I grew up in the inner city,"},{"time":93096,"text":"and there were kids who were failing"},{"time":97983,"text":"in schools 56 years ago when I first went to school,"},{"time":104517,"text":"and those schools are still lousy today, 56 years later."},{"time":111291,"text":"And you know something about a lousy school?"},{"time":113275,"text":"It's not like a bottle of wine."},{"time":115891,"text":"Right? (Laughter)"},{"time":117202,"text":"Where you say, like, '87 was like a good year, right?"},{"time":120980,"text":"That's now how this thing -- I mean, every single year,"},{"time":124096,"text":"it's still the same approach, right?"},{"time":126502,"text":"One size fits all, if you get it, fine, and if you don't,"},{"time":131061,"text":"tough luck. Just tough luck."},{"time":134721,"text":"Why haven't we allowed innovation to happen?"},{"time":137666,"text":"Do not tell me we can't do better than this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":140131,"text":"Look, you go into a place that's failed kids for 50 years,"},{"time":145596,"text":"and you say, \"So what's the plan?\""},{"time":148060,"text":"And they say, \"We'll, we're going to do"},{"time":150164,"text":"what we did last year this year.\""},{"time":153180,"text":"What kind of business model is that?"},{"time":155983,"text":"Banks used to open and operate between 10 and 3."},{"time":161961,"text":"They operated 10 to 3. They were closed for lunch hour."},{"time":167074,"text":"Now, who can bank between 10 and 3? The unemployed."},{"time":172007,"text":"They don't need banks. They got no money in the banks."},{"time":175395,"text":"Who created that business model? Right?"},{"time":178781,"text":"And it went on for decades."},{"time":180894,"text":"You know why? Because they didn't care."},{"time":182809,"text":"It wasn't about the customers."},{"time":184793,"text":"It was about bankers. They created something that worked for them."},{"time":190311,"text":"How could you go to the bank"},{"time":192390,"text":"when you were at work? It didn't matter."},{"time":194799,"text":"And they don't care whether or not Geoff is upset"},{"time":197422,"text":"he can't go to the bank. Go find another bank."},{"time":200011,"text":"They all operate the same way. Right?"},{"time":203449,"text":"Now, one day, some crazy banker had an idea."},{"time":207312,"text":"Maybe we should keep the bank open when people come home from work."},{"time":211289,"text":"They might like that. What about a Saturday?"},{"time":214416,"text":"What about introducing technology?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":217384,"text":"Now look, I'm a technology fan, but I have to admit"},{"time":219603,"text":"to you all I'm a little old."},{"time":221944,"text":"So I was a little slow, and I did not trust technology,"},{"time":224897,"text":"and when they first came out with those new contraptions,"},{"time":228795,"text":"these tellers that you put in a card and they give you money,"},{"time":232465,"text":"I was like, \"There's no way that machine is going to count that money right."},{"time":236080,"text":"I am never using that, right?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":238428,"text":"So technology has changed. Things have changed."},{"time":244363,"text":"Yet not in education. Why?"},{"time":247049,"text":"Why is it that when we had rotary phones,"},{"time":252009,"text":"when we were having folks being crippled by polio,"},{"time":256320,"text":"that we were teaching"},{"time":259417,"text":"the same way then that we're doing right now?"},{"time":261672,"text":"And if you come up with a plan to change things,"},{"time":266080,"text":"people consider you radical."},{"time":268341,"text":"They will say the worst things about you."},{"time":270732,"text":"I said one day, well, look, if the science says --"},{"time":274624,"text":"this is science, not me -- that our poorest children"},{"time":278283,"text":"lose ground in the summertime --"},{"time":281593,"text":"You see where they are in June and say, okay, they're there."},{"time":283695,"text":"You look at them in September, they've gone down."},{"time":286372,"text":"You say, whoo! So I heard about that in '75"},{"time":290588,"text":"when I was at the Ed School at Harvard."},{"time":292219,"text":"I said, \"Oh, wow, this is an important study.\""},{"time":295109,"text":"Because it suggests we should do something."},{"time":299119,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":302684,"text":"Every 10 years they reproduce the same study."},{"time":305788,"text":"It says exactly the same thing:"},{"time":307411,"text":"Poor kids lose ground in the summertime."},{"time":309677,"text":"The system decides you can't run schools in the summer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":314510,"text":"You know, I always wonder, who makes up those rules?"},{"time":317736,"text":"For years I went to -- Look, I went the Harvard Ed School."},{"time":320307,"text":"I thought I knew something."},{"time":321415,"text":"They said it was the agrarian calendar, and people had â€”"},{"time":324496,"text":"but let me tell you why that doesn't make sense."},{"time":326078,"text":"I never got that. I never got that,"},{"time":329360,"text":"because anyone knows if you farm,"},{"time":331512,"text":"you don't plant crops in July and August."},{"time":334587,"text":"You plant them in the spring."},{"time":337336,"text":"So who came up with this idea? Who owns it?"},{"time":341105,"text":"Why did we ever do it?"},{"time":342788,"text":"Well it just turns out in the 1840s we did have,"},{"time":345086,"text":"schools were open all year. They were open all year,"},{"time":348064,"text":"because we had a lot of folks who had to work all day."},{"time":351088,"text":"They didn't have any place for their kids to go."},{"time":352435,"text":"It was a perfect place to have schools."},{"time":354469,"text":"So this is not something that is ordained"},{"time":357360,"text":"from the education gods."}]},{"cues":[{"time":360354,"text":"So why don't we? Why don't we?"},{"time":362530,"text":"Because our business has refused to use science."},{"time":368480,"text":"Science. You have Bill Gates coming out and saying,"},{"time":371492,"text":"\"Look, this works, right? We can do this.\""},{"time":374592,"text":"How many places in America are going to change? None."},{"time":379741,"text":"None. Okay, yeah, there are two. All right?"},{"time":382453,"text":"Yes, there'll be some place, because some folks will do the right thing."},{"time":387239,"text":"As a profession, we have to stop this. The science is clear."}]},{"cues":[{"time":391784,"text":"Here's what we know."},{"time":394079,"text":"We know that the problem begins immediately."},{"time":400054,"text":"Right? This idea, zero to three."},{"time":403963,"text":"My wife, Yvonne, and I, we have four kids,"},{"time":406449,"text":"three grown ones and a 15-year-old."},{"time":409956,"text":"That's a longer story."},{"time":411443,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":413092,"text":"With our first kids, we did not know the science"},{"time":416171,"text":"about brain development."},{"time":418011,"text":"We didn't know how critical those first three years were."},{"time":420625,"text":"We didn't know what was happening in those young brains."},{"time":423039,"text":"We didn't know the role that language,"},{"time":425593,"text":"a stimulus and response, call and response,"},{"time":428484,"text":"how important that was in developing those children."},{"time":431113,"text":"We know that now. What are we doing about it? Nothing."},{"time":435978,"text":"Wealthy people know. Educated people know."},{"time":440074,"text":"And their kids have an advantage."},{"time":441744,"text":"Poor people don't know,"},{"time":443331,"text":"and we're not doing anything to help them at all."},{"time":446335,"text":"But we know this is critical."}]},{"cues":[{"time":447680,"text":"Now, you take pre-kindergarten."},{"time":451410,"text":"We know it's important for kids."},{"time":453480,"text":"Poor kids need that experience."},{"time":456854,"text":"Nope. Lots of places, it doesn't exist."},{"time":461783,"text":"We know health services matter."},{"time":464331,"text":"You know, we provide health services"},{"time":465928,"text":"and people are always fussing at me about, you know,"},{"time":468867,"text":"because I'm all into accountability and data"},{"time":472782,"text":"and all of that good stuff, but we do health services,"},{"time":475976,"text":"and I have to raise a lot of money."},{"time":477217,"text":"People used to say when they'd come fund us,"},{"time":479034,"text":"\"Geoff, why do you provide these health services?\""},{"time":481813,"text":"I used to make stuff up. Right?"},{"time":483922,"text":"I'd say, \"Well, you know a child"},{"time":486473,"text":"who has cavities is not going to, uh,"},{"time":490226,"text":"be able to study as well.\""},{"time":492286,"text":"And I had to because I had to raise the money."},{"time":496291,"text":"But now I'm older, and you know what I tell them?"},{"time":498843,"text":"You know why I provide kids with those health benefits"},{"time":501585,"text":"and the sports and the recreation and the arts?"},{"time":503525,"text":"Because I actually like kids."},{"time":507019,"text":"I actually like kids. (Laughter) (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":512380,"text":"But when they really get pushy, people really get pushy,"},{"time":515555,"text":"I say, \"I do it because you do it for your kid.\""},{"time":518651,"text":"And you've never read a study from MIT that says"},{"time":521643,"text":"giving your kid dance instruction"},{"time":524619,"text":"is going to help them do algebra better,"},{"time":527536,"text":"but you will give that kid dance instruction,"},{"time":529611,"text":"and you will be thrilled that that kid wants to do dance instruction,"},{"time":533124,"text":"and it will make your day. And why shouldn't poor kids"},{"time":536445,"text":"have the same opportunity? It's the floor for these children."},{"time":541999,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":544701,"text":"So here's the other thing."},{"time":547673,"text":"I'm a tester guy. I believe you need data, you need information,"},{"time":551540,"text":"because you work at something, you think it's working,"},{"time":553705,"text":"and you find out it's not working."},{"time":556442,"text":"I mean, you're educators. You work, you say,"},{"time":558308,"text":"you think you've got it, great, no? And you find out they didn't get it."},{"time":561353,"text":"But here's the problem with testing."},{"time":563922,"text":"The testing that we do --"},{"time":566187,"text":"we're going to have our test in New York next week â€”"},{"time":568906,"text":"is in April."},{"time":570861,"text":"You know when we're going to get the results back?"},{"time":573787,"text":"Maybe July, maybe June."},{"time":576954,"text":"And the results have great data."},{"time":579762,"text":"They'll tell you Raheem really struggled,"},{"time":582839,"text":"couldn't do two-digit multiplication -- so great data,"},{"time":586217,"text":"but you're getting it back after school is over."},{"time":588746,"text":"And so, what do you do?"},{"time":591229,"text":"You go on vacation. (Laughter)"},{"time":594431,"text":"You come back from vacation."},{"time":595766,"text":"Now you've got all of this test data from last year."},{"time":601216,"text":"You don't look at it."},{"time":603569,"text":"Why would you look at it?"},{"time":605832,"text":"You're going to go and teach this year."},{"time":607991,"text":"So how much money did we just spend on all of that?"},{"time":611243,"text":"Billions and billions of dollars"},{"time":614246,"text":"for data that it's too late to use."},{"time":617303,"text":"I need that data in September."},{"time":619129,"text":"I need that data in November."},{"time":620900,"text":"I need to know you're struggling, and I need to know"},{"time":622908,"text":"whether or not what I did corrected that."},{"time":625293,"text":"I need to know that this week."},{"time":627274,"text":"I don't need to know that at the end of the year when it's too late."}]},{"cues":[{"time":630853,"text":"Because in my older years, I've become somewhat of a clairvoyant."},{"time":636043,"text":"I can predict school scores."},{"time":639266,"text":"You take me to any school."},{"time":641311,"text":"I'm really good at inner city schools that are struggling."},{"time":644369,"text":"And you tell me last year 48 percent of those kids"},{"time":648184,"text":"were on grade level."},{"time":650791,"text":"And I say, \"Okay, what's the plan, what did we do"},{"time":652685,"text":"from last year to this year?\""},{"time":653634,"text":"You say, \"We're doing the same thing.\""},{"time":655449,"text":"I'm going to make a prediction. (Laughter)"},{"time":658204,"text":"This year, somewhere between 44"},{"time":661370,"text":"and 52 percent of those kids will be on grade level."},{"time":664265,"text":"And I will be right every single time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":667840,"text":"So we're spending all of this money, but we're getting what?"},{"time":672229,"text":"Teachers need real information right now"},{"time":674821,"text":"about what's happening to their kids."},{"time":676410,"text":"The high stakes is today, because you can do something about it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":681803,"text":"So here's the other issue that I just think"},{"time":686637,"text":"we've got to be concerned about."},{"time":689445,"text":"We can't stifle innovation in our business."},{"time":693725,"text":"We have to innovate. And people in our business get mad about innovation."},{"time":697618,"text":"They get angry if you do something different."},{"time":699605,"text":"If you try something new, people are always like,"},{"time":701382,"text":"\"Ooh, charter schools.\" Hey, let's try some stuff. Let's see."},{"time":705879,"text":"This stuff hasn't worked for 55 years."},{"time":708240,"text":"Let's try something different. And here's the rub."},{"time":711311,"text":"Some of it's not going to work."},{"time":713403,"text":"You know, people tell me, \"Yeah, those charter schools, a lot of them don't work.\""},{"time":716141,"text":"A lot of them don't. They should be closed."},{"time":719609,"text":"I mean, I really believe they should be closed."},{"time":721515,"text":"But we can't confuse figuring out the science"},{"time":725824,"text":"and things not working with we shouldn't therefore do anything."},{"time":730600,"text":"Right? Because that's not the way the world works."}]},{"cues":[{"time":732502,"text":"If you think about technology,"},{"time":734008,"text":"imagine if that's how we thought about technology."},{"time":736522,"text":"Every time something didn't work,"},{"time":737819,"text":"we just threw in the towel and said, \"Let's forget it.\" Right?"},{"time":740365,"text":"You know, they convinced me. I'm sure some of you were like me --"},{"time":743534,"text":"the latest and greatest thing, the PalmPilot."},{"time":748059,"text":"They told me, \"Geoff, if you get this PalmPilot"},{"time":750538,"text":"you'll never need another thing.\""},{"time":752491,"text":"That thing lasted all of three weeks. It was over."},{"time":756932,"text":"I was so disgusted I spent my money on this thing."},{"time":760691,"text":"Did anybody stop inventing? Not a person. Not a soul."},{"time":766608,"text":"The folks went out there. They kept inventing."},{"time":769112,"text":"The fact that you have failure, that shouldn't stop you"},{"time":772222,"text":"from pushing the science forward."}]},{"cues":[{"time":775108,"text":"Our job as educators,"},{"time":777280,"text":"there's some stuff we know that we can do."},{"time":779745,"text":"And we've got to do better. The evaluation, we have to start with kids earlier,"},{"time":783724,"text":"we have to make sure that we provide the support to young people."},{"time":786648,"text":"We've got to give them all of these opportunities."},{"time":789056,"text":"So that we have to do. But this innovation issue,"},{"time":792372,"text":"this idea that we've got to keep innovating"},{"time":796164,"text":"until we really nail this science down"},{"time":799088,"text":"is something that is absolutely critical."}]},{"cues":[{"time":801296,"text":"And this is something, by the way,"},{"time":803520,"text":"that I think is going to be a challenge for our entire field."},{"time":807055,"text":"America cannot wait another 50 years to get this right."},{"time":812334,"text":"We have run out of time."},{"time":815003,"text":"I don't know about a fiscal cliff, but I know there's an educational cliff"},{"time":818091,"text":"that we are walking over right this very second,"},{"time":821544,"text":"and if we allow folks to continue this foolishness"},{"time":825984,"text":"about saying we can't afford this â€”"},{"time":828946,"text":"So Bill Gates says it's going to cost five billion dollars."},{"time":831192,"text":"What is five billion dollars to the United States?"},{"time":833752,"text":"What did we spend in Afghanistan this year?"},{"time":836425,"text":"How many trillions? (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":840392,"text":"When the country cares about something,"},{"time":843416,"text":"we'll spend a trillion dollars without blinking an eye."},{"time":847065,"text":"When the safety of America is threatened,"},{"time":850009,"text":"we will spend any amount of money."},{"time":852880,"text":"The real safety of our nation"},{"time":855936,"text":"is preparing this next generation"},{"time":858313,"text":"so that they can take our place"},{"time":860552,"text":"and be the leaders of the world"},{"time":864739,"text":"when it comes to thinking and technology and democracy"},{"time":867936,"text":"and all that stuff we care about."},{"time":870313,"text":"I dare say it's a pittance,"},{"time":874858,"text":"what it would require for us to really"},{"time":878543,"text":"begin to solve some of these problems."}]},{"cues":[{"time":880791,"text":"So once we do that, I'll no longer be angry. (Laughter)"},{"time":886180,"text":"So, you guys, help me get there."},{"time":891975,"text":"Thank you all very much. Thank you."},{"time":894304,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":903627,"text":"John Legend: So what is the high school dropout rate at Harlem Children's Zone?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":907835,"text":"Geoffrey Canada: Well, you know, John,"},{"time":909302,"text":"100 percent of our kids graduated high school"},{"time":911625,"text":"last year in my school."},{"time":912776,"text":"A hundred percent of them went to college."},{"time":914244,"text":"This year's seniors will have 100 percent graduating high school."},{"time":917634,"text":"Last I heard we had 93 percent accepted to college."},{"time":920696,"text":"We'd better get that other seven percent."},{"time":923310,"text":"So that's just how this goes. (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":930005,"text":"JL: So how do you stick with them after they leave high school?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":932598,"text":"GC: Well, you know, one of the bad problems"},{"time":935187,"text":"we have in this country is these kids, the same kids,"},{"time":937629,"text":"these same vulnerable kids, when you get them in school,"},{"time":939558,"text":"they drop out in record numbers."},{"time":940900,"text":"And so we've figured out that you've got to really design"},{"time":944565,"text":"a network of support for these kids that in many ways"},{"time":947989,"text":"mimics what a good parent does."},{"time":950454,"text":"They harass you, right? They call you, they say,"},{"time":953551,"text":"\"I want to see your grades. How'd you do on that last test?"},{"time":955662,"text":"What are you talking about that you want to leave school?"},{"time":958625,"text":"And you're not coming back here.\""},{"time":959915,"text":"So a bunch of my kids know you can't come back to Harlem"},{"time":962170,"text":"because Geoff is looking for you."},{"time":963501,"text":"They're like, \"I really can't come back.\" No. You'd better stay in school."},{"time":966804,"text":"But I'm not kidding about some of this,"},{"time":969630,"text":"and it gets a little bit to the grit issue."},{"time":971426,"text":"When kids know that you refuse to let them fail,"},{"time":975620,"text":"it puts a different pressure on them,"},{"time":977524,"text":"and they don't give up as easy."},{"time":979212,"text":"So sometimes they don't have it inside,"},{"time":981654,"text":"and they're, like, \"You know, I don't want to do this,"},{"time":983700,"text":"but I know my mother's going to be mad.\""},{"time":987053,"text":"Well, that matters to kids, and it helps get them through."},{"time":989782,"text":"We try to create a set of strategies that gets them tutoring"},{"time":993591,"text":"and help and support, but also a set of encouragements"},{"time":997526,"text":"that say to them, \"You can do it. It is going to be hard,"},{"time":1000136,"text":"but we refuse to let you fail.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":1002194,"text":"JL: Well, thank you Dr. Canada."},{"time":1003774,"text":"Please give it up for him one more time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1005438,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}